window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Life as a baron is great....</b></p> <p><b>Well, mostly great...</b></p> <p>Mason could probably do with fewer murderous monsters, like acid-spitting spiders and giant fire titans, but he makes due. His village is well defended, his metallic creations get more epic by the day, and his women are relatively safe and healthy, so Mason spends some well-deserved time getting to know Baroness Batonova a little better. </p> <p>But war is coming to Illaria whether they want it to or not.</p>"; 
